
# ## GitHub
#
# https://docs.github.com/en/issues/tracking-your-work-with-issues/using-issues/linking-a-pull-request-to-an-issue#linking-a-pull-request-to-an-issue-using-a-keyword
#
# > close, closes, closed, fix, fixes, fixed, resolve, resolves, resolved
#
# ## sourcehut:
# https://man.sr.ht/git.sr.ht/#referencing-tickets-in-git-commit-messages
#
# Add the appropriate Git trailer for the resolution.
# Supported trailer examples:
# * Fixes: https://todo.sr.ht/~svbn/foobar/123
# * Implements: https://todo.sr.ht/~svbn/foobar/123
# * References: https://todo.sr.ht/~svbn/foobar/123
# * Closes: https://todo.sr.ht/~svbn/foobar/123
#
# ## Commit message thoughts
